description:
'Last Day of Summer' is a split album from dark UK instrumentalists Sons of Alpha Centauri and West Virginia Riff Rock outfit Treasure Cat (featuring members of Karma to Burn). Includes 3 exclusive tracks from Alpha Cat - the lethal collaboration of both bands rocking together plus all new material from both acts.

This limited and rare tour package is: 

 - A copy of the 'Last Day of Summer' album;
 - The promotional release poster from Underdogma Records;
 - Two SOAC badges and; 
 - Karma to Burn / Sons of Alpha Centauri London 2009 show poster when the CD was released
